text.data-name: 3% of your basic pay is deposited into the traditional balance of your TSP account each pay period.
Next, your agency/service matches your 3% contribution dollar-for-dollar.
The next 2% will be matched at 50¢ on the dollar.
That’s $250 biweekly towards your retirement goal.
Don’t leave free money on the table!
